    "In other words, SFA improves the efficiency 24 and accuracy of the neural code and hence optimizes information transmission 25.",
    "SFA can be seen as an adaptation of the spike output range to the statistical range of the environment, meaning that it contrasts fluctuations of the input rather than its absolute intensity 26.",
    "Thereby noise is reduced and, as mentioned above, repetitive information is suppressed which leads to an increase in entropy.",
    "Consequently, the detection of a salient stimulus can be enhanced 27.",
    "These biological advantages of SFA can also be exploited for low-power and high-entropy computations in artificial neural networks."
